findings.title: No Max Transaction and Holding Modify function found
findings.description: The contract does not have a function to limit the maximum transaction amount or modify holdings, which can lead to honeypot risks if exploited.

findings.title: No Transaction Limiter Function Found
findings.description: The contract does not have a function to limit the number of overall token transactions, which may cause honeypot risk.

findings.title: Honeypot Risk
findings.description: The contract has a honeypot risk due to various functions that can limit or block transactions, causing users to lose their tokens.
